      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable daily driver that's ready for its next chapter? This car is in fair condition and offers a fantastic, reliable ride for anyone looking for great value! While it shows some honest signs of use and age, it has plenty of life left and performs consistently on the road. It\u2019s a wonderful opportunity to own a solid vehicle at a budget-friendly price point!",
